<p>I loved this part:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>A focus in media coverage during the off season will be sensationalist stories designed to increase everyday paranoia and form habits in viewers conductive to personal safety.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I strongly wish this part wasn't blocked out as I want to know what this effect is called!</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Victims of this effect (known as the R█████ effect, in honor of the late Doctor R█████)</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I think this quote breaks the tone a bit and doesn't really fit in here (imo):</p>
